### Search Service Workers - Basic Search
POST {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10,
  "searchTerm": "",
  "serviceNames": [],
  "languages": [],
  "minHourlyRate": null,
  "maxHourlyRate": null,
  "latitude": null,
  "longitude": null,
  "radiusKm": 50.0,
  "sortBy": "Distance",
  "sortDirection": "Ascending",
  "minRating": null,
  "verifiedOnly": null,
  "availableOnly": true
}

### Search Service Workers - Location-based Search (London coordinates)
POST {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10,
  "searchTerm": "cleaning",
  "serviceNames": ["House Cleaning", "Window Cleaning", "Deep Cleaning"],
  "languages": ["English", "Spanish"],
  "minHourlyRate": 15.00,
  "maxHourlyRate": 50.00,
  "latitude": 51.5074,
  "longitude": -0.1278,
  "radiusKm": 25.0,
  "sortBy": "Distance",
  "sortDirection": "Ascending",
  "minRating": 4,
  "verifiedOnly": true,
  "availableOnly": true
}

### Search Service Workers - Multiple Services Search
POST {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 15,
  "searchTerm": "",
  "serviceNames": ["Babysitting", "Pet Care", "Tutoring"],
  "languages": ["English", "French", "German"],
  "minHourlyRate": null,
  "maxHourlyRate": null,
  "latitude": null,
  "longitude": null,
  "radiusKm": 50.0,
  "sortBy": "HourlyRate",
  "sortDirection": "Ascending",
  "minRating": null,
  "verifiedOnly": null,
  "availableOnly": true
}

### Search Service Workers - Rate-based Search
POST {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 20,
  "searchTerm": "",
  "serviceNames": [],
  "languages": [],
  "minHourlyRate": 20.00,
  "maxHourlyRate": 40.00,
  "latitude": null,
  "longitude": null,
  "radiusKm": 50.0,
  "sortBy": "HourlyRate",
  "sortDirection": "Ascending",
  "minRating": null,
  "verifiedOnly": null,
  "availableOnly": true
}

### Search Service Workers - By Name and Rating
POST {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10,
  "searchTerm": "john",
  "serviceNames": [],
  "languages": [],
  "minHourlyRate": null,
  "maxHourlyRate": null,
  "latitude": null,
  "longitude": null,
  "radiusKm": 50.0,
  "sortBy": "Rating",
  "sortDirection": "Descending",
  "minRating": 3,
  "verifiedOnly": false,
  "availableOnly": true
}

### Get Service Worker by ID
GET {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/1

### Get Service Worker by User ID
GET {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/by-user/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

### Get Profile Completion Status (Requires Authentication)
GET {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/profile-status/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Update Service Worker Profile (Requires Authentication)
PUT {{SafeHabour.API_HostAddress}}/api/serviceworkers/update
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="UserId"

12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="FirstName"

John
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="LastName"

Doe
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Bio"

Experienced house cleaner with 5+ years of experience.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="HourlyRate"

25.50
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--
